  <brief_title>Topical Ocular Mecamylamine in Diabetic Macular Edema (DME)</brief_title>
  <official_title>Phase 2 Study of the Safety and Bioactivity of Topical Ocular Mecamylamine for the Treatment of Diabetic Macular Edema (DME)</official_title>
