  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is an open-label study evaluating the safety and tolerability of topical ocular
      mecamylamine given twice a day in patients with diabetic macular edema (DME). Patients will
      be treated for 12 weeks.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
